    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - CAB - TILT: 9800 - MAINTENANCE - WINDSHIELD WASHER</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="pm" graphiccount="0">
        <title>WINDSHIELD WASHER</title>
        <para>A minimum of service is required to assure continued washer operation. Keep reservoir filled with the
            recommended windshield washer solvent or equivalent and keep the wiper nozzles clean. If dirt enters
            reservoir, remove at once and flush out with clean water. Refill reservoir with solvent after flushing.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
